        <p class="text-text leading-relaxed mb-4">To summarize the above, the sludge discharge cycle time is crucial for operating a self-cleaning disc-stack centrifuge.</p>
        <p class="text-text leading-relaxed mb-4">With the calculator and formula provided in this article, a centrifuge operator should determine the optimum cycle time between sludge discharges and get the maximum efficiency out of the centrifuge.</p>
